headline.main: Smith Scores Short-Handed to Lift Senators Over Jackets 3-2
headline.print_headline: Smith Scores Short-Handed to Lift Senators Over Jackets 3-2

lead_paragraph: The Ottawa Senators got a tough contest from one of the league's best teams and had enough to come out the winners.
